laboratory_examinations.findings: Dilated appendix measuring up to 9 cm with surrounding fat stranding. No appendicolith and no evidence of perforation. Liver, pancreas, spleen, kidneys, gallbladder, adrenals, and visualized loops of small bowel appear normal. A cyst in the left mid pole of the kidney and a right adnexal cyst measuring 2.4 cm are noted.
